    public class Tag<T1,T2>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Input<T1>, Output<T2>
    Represents a transition "tag" in a FSMIO. A tag is made of an input (that activates the transition) and of an output (issued after the transition is executed).

    ioannis.parissis@grenoble-inp.fr
